notes.title: Author Contributions
notes.p: J. Espinoza, A.U., L.B., and A.Q. designed the research; J. Echevería, J. Espinoza and A.U. analyzed the chemical data; J. Espinoza and L.B. performed the bioassays; J. Espinoza and M.G.-T. performed the statistical analyses; J. Echeverría, A.U., and M.G.-T. wrote the paper; and all of the authors read and approved the final manuscript.
